headline.main: Syria Talks Set to End With 'Agreed Agenda'-Diplomats
headline.print_headline: Syria Talks Set to End With 'Agreed Agenda'-Diplomats

lead_paragraph: U.S. jets carried out dozens of airstrikes on al-Qaida targets in Yemen overnight and in the past 48 hours in one of the lengthiest, sustained operations inside this conflict-torn Arab country, Yemeni officials and residents said Friday.
